User
    ident Text
    password Password
    email Text
    bio Text Maybe
    image Text Maybe
    UniqueUser ident
    UniqueEmail email
    deriving Typeable
Comment json -- Adding "json" causes ToJSON and FromJSON instances to be derived.
    message Text
    userId UserId Maybe
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show
Following
  followed UserId
  follower UserId
  UniqueFollowing followed follower
  deriving Eq
  deriving Show

